Class Robot

  • java.lang.Object
    • androidsrus.Robot

  • public class Robot
extends java.lang.Object
    An object of class Robot holds the robot's model, serial number, its brain parts, its mobility parts, its vision parts, its arms parts, its media center parts and its power plant parts
